    <item>
      <title>特朗普的目标不仅是佐治亚州的选票，还有对选举的信任</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/03/us/politics/trump-georgia-doubt-election-integrity.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统已派出 260 名联邦调查局 (FBI) 人员。分析人士向佐治亚州重复了他毫无根据的关于 2020 年欺诈的指控。但批评者表示，此举的目的是破坏人们对选举进程的整体信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/03/us/politics/trump-georgia-doubt-election-integrity.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 23:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
